  m_text: "\u26A0\uFE0F You were going to college to build your future...\nnot to
    destroy it.\n\nDon't make your parents regret raising you.\nFollow the traffic
    rules. Be safe on the road.\n\nThey are waiting for you at home.\nThey are proud
    of you.\nDon't break their hearts.\n\n. . . . . . . . . .\n\nCongratulations.\n\nYou
    left your parents alone forever.\nNo more college. No more future.\nNo more coming
    home.\n\n\U0001FAA6 Good Afterlife."
